Releasing a New Version
=======================

 * Do final quality checks
   $ pep8 shinken
 * Bump version numbers
   - setup.py
   - debian/changelog
 * Update NEWS and TODO
 * Commit changes
   $ git commit -a -m "Update to X.Y.Z"
   $ git tag -s "X.Y.Z"
   $ git push
   $ git push --tags
 * Upload and announce

